Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:05.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(200,200)}同じ二人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:15.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(200,200)}まばたく刹那　君を想うよ
